task.summary: Added save/load emote list through jsonpickle module. Also removed references to UserMap for the moment.
Changed frequency output to embed, added per-guild emoji tracking, and added owner-only check to kill. Also added packages for interactions (future endeavor).
Added very basic queue feature. Todo: Mark voice channel for invite, delete queue message after amount of time, argument for user limit.

Queue now waits for reaction and can timeout without activity instead of relying on every on_reaction_add event. Also added SystemExit exception to on_message event (which would throw error when sending kill command response).
Removed error handling from on_message (it didn't work) and refactored queue reaction check function.
